    <div class="QH">
      <h4 class="QH-Title">Quality Policy</h4>
      <p class="QH-Para">Our quality check begins right from the moment we choose our raw material. We carefully select
        and test our raw materials daily at our in-house lab. The entire process of manufacturing is keenly supervised
        from pre to post production. Utmost care is taken to ensure the guarantee of quality, hygiene, and taste. We
        have engineered a unique technique and process to fulfill the demand for high quantity production while
        maintaining the parameters for taste and quality.</p>

      <h4 class="QH-Title">Ingredient Selection</h4>
      <p class="QH-Para">A standardized process has been installed to keep a check on the selection of the ingredients
        as we believe that the right ingredients are the most crucial part of the manufacturing. Our suppliers have been
        providing us with their services for decades and are familiar with the quality requirements for the brand. The
        ingredients are tested in our in-house lab using contemporary technology to give you the tastiest product.</p>

      <h4 class="QH-Title">Preservation</h4>
      <p class="QH-Para">Preservation is just as necessary as manufacturing. Both the raw materials and finished
        products require preservation as it gets distributed from various channels during their shelf life. Our
        streamlined process helps us with maintaining high levels of product movements on a daily basis. We have adopted
        some new technologies while maintaining some old tried and tested hard customs to maintain the supply chain of
        fresh products.</p>


      <h4 class="QH-Title">Quality Check</h4>
      <p class="QH-Para">Quality marks the identity of your product and we learned this early on our way into the
        business, Thus, we have developed a process to keep a tab on the journey of our products. It begins at the
        testing of our raw materials and goes beyond providing ITC’s ECF(Elemental Chlorine Free) USA FDA standard paper
        packing for the finished products.</p>




    </div>
